<details class="tool-instructions">
  <summary>Install</summary>
  <ol>
    <li>Download <code>Rev Bump.jsx</code></li>
    <li>Copy it to your After Effects scripts folder:<br>
      <code>C:\Program Files\Adobe\Adobe After Effects &lt;version&gt;\Support Files\Scripts\ScriptUI Panels\</code><br>
      (requires admin / Run as Administrator)
    </li>
    <li>Restart After Effects</li>
    <li>Open via <strong>Window &rarr; Rev Bump</strong> &mdash; docks like any native panel</li>
  </ol>
</details>
<details class="tool-instructions">
  <summary>Features</summary>
  <ul class="tool-shortcuts">
    <li><strong>Letter Bump</strong> Increments the letter segment of the filename (A &rarr; B, B &rarr; C&hellip;) and saves as a new .aep</li>
    <li><strong>Number Bump</strong> Increments the version number (v01 &rarr; v02) and saves as a new .aep</li>
    <li><strong>Live preview</strong> Shows what the new filename will be before you commit</li>
    <li><strong>Comp rename</strong> Automatically renames the matching comp inside the project to stay in sync</li>
    <li><strong>Flexible naming</strong> Supports filenames with or without a middle segment (e.g. <code>Project_A_Navy_v01</code> or <code>Project_A_v01</code>)</li>
    <li><strong>Overwrite guard</strong> Prompts before overwriting an existing file</li>
  </ul>
</details>
